{"tid":1263752,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］只係去個廁所，返到公司發覺門已鎖，點算好","createTime":"2019-06-28T10:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T01:00:07.000Z","uid":171451,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"02617df5a369561072375e6fe480e55d5068ee0c","tid":1263752,"uid":171451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的，公司係放6點，咁臨收工時突然想開大就去廁所，咁嗰時係有個同事喺公司，老闆出差。<br />\n<br />\n之後咁arm有個電話黎，傾左陣，返到公司門口發覺燈關曬，禁密碼都入唔倒，應該係鎖左，call 爆同事電話都無人聽，我所有銀包，袋都喺公司到，手頭上只有呢部電話同廁所鎖匙，一個仙都無。<br />\n<br />\n同層無個識，而家的我，望住公司門口，除左call 爆同事電話，真係唔知做咩好⋯⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f0b015af0bad3510608f78419cb3f7fdef32ef","tid":1263752,"uid":268497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:46:57.000Z","msg":"搵朋友 屋企人救你 另外同保安熟絡嗎?"},{"pid":"fd1ab20dea1fd5ede8f62faeb0716a9f14772b2e","tid":1263752,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:48:06.000Z","msg":"影張相黎睇下先啦"},{"pid":"d72d57b488c76a5afe6d9365217ef241e6e66df4","tid":1263752,"uid":174013,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"返入去廁所坐到星期一"},{"pid":"36eefb08b55a57d3fe2bd19add56336d19401e7c","tid":1263752,"uid":20514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:51:53.000Z","msg":"Call Uber 返屋企先囉"},{"pid":"b677cd07fcdc9ad7c1999ab65024f132b14a9e17","tid":1263752,"uid":46927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d72d57b488c76a5afe6d9365217ef241e6e66df4","tid":1263752,"uid":174013,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"返入去廁所坐到星期一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:52:10.000Z","msg":"紅日"},{"pid":"8114815c5c3e95354461d0573ccf690767082c33","tid":1263752,"uid":169116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:16:51.000Z","msg":"係女嘅話我收留你.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係男嘅就撞門啦~~<img src=